snippet.title: Snowball! - iOS / Android Game Trailer HD 1080p
snippet.description:
Snowball! - iOS / Android Game Trailer HD 1080p

App Store - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/snowball!!/id1174489793?mt=8

Google Play Store - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.noodlecake.snowball&hl=en

Description
Snowball is a homegrown, hand-cranked winter pinball adventure from Pixeljam, the creators of Dino Run.

Send your behemoth snow spheres through an epic kid-constructed bobsled maze of snowbanks, homemade wooden paddles, Tesla coils, igloos, railcars, and more.

For both casual and hardcore pinball fans!

Planned Updates:
-Night / Expert Mode
-New Music
-Gyroscopic Time Attack!
